OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start to the
OL,6,Fday, but blue skies returning through
OL,7,Fthe morning as the cloud clears away.
OL,8,FA hot and sunny afternoon to come,
OL,9,Fwith light winds across the region. A
OL,10,Flittle cooler towards the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPlenty of sunshine to end the
OL,13,Fday. Dry overnight, with increasing
OL,14,Famounts of cloud cover once more, with
OL,15,Fsome hill fog possible in places.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FMorning cloud clearing to
OL,18,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,19,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,20,Fafternoon. Temperatures a little lower
OL,21,Fas winds turn northerly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
