OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fdry into the weekend, with sunny
OL,7,Fspells by day and clear skies at
OL,8,Fnight. Temperatures trending a little
OL,9,Fnearer to average, but still feeling
OL,10,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
